caption:
Meet Anissa "Donny" Truitt, the Founder & CEO of @17thandGranville! 17th & Granville is a #BlackOwned clothing brand celebrating the beauty and uniqueness of all people, especially those in the BIPOC and LGBTQ+ communities. Inspired by Donny's personal experiences and the lack of representation in the fashion industry, the brand creates inclusive collections that resonate with underrepresented individuals.⁠
⁠
Follow @17thandGranville to support and shop their latest collection 🙌🏾
